thread.title: BRIEF-Digital Realty Expects To Deliver 2018 Core FFO Per Share In A Range Of $6.45-$6.60​

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Digital Realty Expects To Deliver 2018 Core FFO Per Share In A Range Of $6.45-$6.60​
text:
Jan 8 (Reuters) - Digital Realty Trust Inc:
* DIGITAL REALTY EXPECTS TO DELIVER 2018 CORE FFO PER SHARE WITHIN A RANGE OF $6.45-$6.60​
* DIGITAL REALTY PROVIDES INITIAL 2018 OUTLOOK AND SCHEDULES 4Q17 EARNINGS RELEASE AND CONFERENCE CALL
* SEES ‍2018 TOTAL REVENUE $3.0 - $3.2 BILLION​ * SEES ‍2018 FUNDS FROM OPERATIONS / SHARE (NAREIT-DEFINED) $6.40 - $6.50​
* FY2018 FFO PER SHARE VIEW $6.54 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
